			CadetMod.Modules.Content.AddEntityState(typeof(MainState));
			CadetMod.Modules.Content.AddEntityState(typeof(BaseCadetState));
			CadetMod.Modules.Content.AddEntityState(typeof(BaseEmote));
			CadetMod.Modules.Content.AddEntityState(typeof(ShootSmg));
			CadetMod.Modules.Content.AddEntityState(typeof(ThrowGun));
			CadetMod.Modules.Content.AddEntityState(typeof(EnterReload));
			CadetMod.Modules.Content.AddEntityState(typeof(EnterReload));
			CadetMod.Modules.Content.AddEntityState(typeof(Reload));
			CadetMod.Modules.Content.AddEntityState(typeof(Rolload));
			CadetMod.Modules.Content.AddEntityState(typeof(SlideLoad));
			CadetMod.Modules.Content.AddEntityState(typeof(FireEcho));
			CadetMod.Modules.Content.AddEntityState(typeof(GrenadeLauncher));
			CadetMod.Modules.Content.AddEntityState(typeof(Shotgun));
			CadetMod.Modules.Content.AddEntityState(typeof(UltraShotgun));
			CadetMod.Modules.Content.AddEntityState(typeof(EmoteBot));
			CadetMod.Modules.Content.AddEntityState(typeof(Rest));
		}
	}
	public static class CadetTokens
	{
		public static void Init()
		{
			AddCadetTokens();
		}

		public static void AddCadetTokens()
		{
			string text = "KENKO_CADET_";
			string text2 = "The Cadet is a versatile gunner who is able to weave through combat with close range weapons and quick mobility.<color=#CCD3E0>" + Environment.NewLine + Environment.NewLine;
			text2 = text2 + "< ! > Make sure to Shoot at a close distance to effectively use your limited ammo count without decreasing your damage." + Environment.NewLine + Environment.NewLine;
			text2 = text2 + "< ! > Plan C increases its damage and radius with your current ammo so make sure to use it when your magazine is full." + Environment.NewLine + Environment.NewLine;
			text2 = text2 + "< ! > Use Replenshing Roll to swiftly avoid burst damage and to fully restock your magazine." + Environment.NewLine + Environment.NewLine;
			text2 = text2 + "< ! > Try to use Echo Drones as often as you can as it will help clear out any enemies you may have missed while on the move." + Environment.NewLine + Environment.NewLine;
			string text3 = "\"Have you ever thought about making a difference in this world? Do you believe you're destined for honor-bound glory? Does your body ache for the adrenaline rush that only life-threatening situations provide? If you answered yes to any of these questions, then consider joining our ranks!\"\r\n\r\nThe barely audible television played in the shelter, a new addition. Perfectly placed in the middle, it was the center of attention to the young impressionable eyes of the area with nothing to lose. Some of them came quickly, automatically entranced by the promise of something better than whatever they called their current situation. Others tried to hold out, fearful of the idea of a military life, although one can only hold out for so long before they don't have any other options left but to swallow whatever complaints they have and roll with it.\r\n\r\nThe rest of them? They either got with the program, or got crushed under the city's rubble. Indecisiveness isn't an option, not in this age at least.\r\n\r\n\"And remember, you'll always have a place here! Visit your local recruitment center today! See you soon, soldier!\"\r\n\r\nYeah. Not an option, never has been.\r\n";
			string text4 = "and he left, an echo of his past self.";
			string text5 = "and he vanished, a waste of passion.";
			Language.Add(text + "NAME", "Cadet");
			Language.Add(text + "DESCRIPTION", text2);
			Language.Add(text + "SUBTITLE", "Aspiring Soldier");
			Language.Add(text + "LORE", text3);
			Language.Add(text + "OUTRO_FLAVOR", text4);
			Language.Add(text + "OUTRO_FAILURE", text5);
			Language.Add(text + "MASTERY_SKIN_NAME", "Lieutenant");
			Language.Add(text + "PASSIVE_NAME", "");
			Language.Add(text + "PASSIVE_DESCRIPTION", ".");
			Language.Add(text + "PRIMARY_SMG_NAME", "Bullet Storm");
			Language.Add(text + "PRIMARY_SMG_DESCRIPTION", "<style=cIsUtility>Agile</style>. " + $"Fire a laser for <style=cIsDamage>{100f * CadetConfig.smgDamageCoefficient.Value}% damage</style>. " + $"Requires a <style=cIsUtility>reload</style> after <style=cIsDamage>{CadetConfig.baseSMGMaxAmmo.Value}</style> bullets.");
			Language.Add(text + "PRIMARY_SHOTGUN_NAME", "Crashing Tides");
			Language.Add(text + "PRIMARY_SHOTGUN_DESCRIPTION", "<style=cIsUtility>Agile</style>. " + $"Fire a burst for <style=cIsDamage>3x{100f * CadetConfig.shotgunDamageCoefficient.Value}% damage</style>. " + $"Requires a <style=cIsUtility>reload</style> after <style=cIsDamage>{CadetConfig.baseShotgunMaxAmmo.Value}</style> bullets.");
			Language.Add(text + "SECONDARY_THROWGUN_NAME", "Plan C");
			Language.Add(text + "SECONDARY_THROWGUN_DESCRIPTION", $"Throw your gun dealing <style=cIsDamage>{100f * CadetConfig.throwGunDamageCoefficient.Value} - " + $"{100f * CadetConfig.throwGunMaxDamageCoefficient.Value}% damage</style> based on your current ammo.");
			Language.Add(text + "SECONDARY_GRENADE_NAME", "Plan B");
			Language.Add(text + "SECONDARY_GRENADE_DESCRIPTION", "Fire your lightweight grenade launcher dealing " + $"<style=cIsDamage>{100f * CadetConfig.grenadeDamageCoefficient.Value}% damage</style>.");
			Language.Add(text + "UTILITY_ROLLOAD_NAME", "Replenishing Roll");
			Language.Add(text + "UTILITY_ROLLOAD_DESCRIPTION", "Roll in a direction instantly <style=cIsUtility>reloading</style> your gun.");
			Language.Add(text + "UTILITY_SLIDE_NAME", "Restocking Reposition");
			Language.Add(text + "UTILITY_SLIDE_DESCRIPTION", "Slide in a direction instantly <style=cIsUtility>reloading</style> your gun.");
			Language.Add(text + "SPECIAL_ULTRA_NAME", "Plan A");
			Language.Add(text + "SPECIAL_ULTRA_DESCRIPTION", "<style=cIsUtility>Agile</style>. Fire a heavy burst of pellets, dealing " + $"<style=cIsDamage>{CadetConfig.superShotgunPelletCount.Value}x{100f * CadetConfig.superShotgunDamageCoefficient.Value}% damage</style>.");
			Language.Add(text + "SPECIAL_ECHO_NAME", "Echo Drones");
			Language.Add(text + "SPECIAL_ECHO_DESCRIPTION", "Fabricate <style=cIsDamage>two drones</style> that seek out nearby enemies dealing " + $"<style=cIsDamage>2x{100f * CadetConfig.echoDronesDamageCoefficient.Value}% damage</style>.");
			Language.Add(Tokens.GetAchievementNameToken("KENKO_CADET_masteryAchievement"), "Cadet: Mastery");
			Language.Add(Tokens.GetAchievementDescriptionToken("KENKO_CADET_masteryAchievement"), "As Cadet, beat the game or obliterate on Monsoon.");
		}
	}
	public static class CadetUnlockables
	{
		public static UnlockableDef characterUnlockableDef;

		public static UnlockableDef masterySkinUnlockableDef;

		public static void Init()
		{
			masterySkinUnlockableDef = CadetMod.Modules.Content.CreateAndAddUnlockbleDef("KENKO_CADET_masteryUnlockable", Tokens.GetAchievementNameToken("KENKO_CADET_masteryAchievement"), CharacterBase<CadetSurvivor>.instance.assetBundle.LoadAsset<Sprite>("texMasterySkin"));
		}
	}
	public static class DamageTypes
	{
		public static ModdedDamageType Default;

		internal static void Init()
		{
			//IL_0001: Unknown result type (might be due to invalid IL or missing references)
			//IL_0006: Unknown result type (might be due to invalid IL or missing references)
			Default = DamageAPI.ReserveDamageType();
